    <abstract>
      <t>&lt;p&gt;This document describes version two of Microsoft's PPP CHAP dialect (MS-CHAP-V2).  MS-CHAP-V2 is similar to, but incompatible with, MS-CHAP version one (MS-CHAP-V1).  This memo provides information for the Internet community.&lt;/p&gt;</t>
